1.20	Lonely_Boy_(film)	Lonely Boy (film)	Lonely Boy is a 1962 cinema verite documentary about former teen sensation Paul Anka. The film takes its name from Anka's hit song, Lonely Boy, which he performs to screaming fans in the film. This short documentary is also unique for its use of hand-held cameras to record intimate backstage moments.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/9/9d/LonelyBoy.jpg
